#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/guide/rest/quick-start.md
msgid "This guide assumes that you use the [API application template](https://github.com/yiisoft/app-api).  It already includes request body parsing, request input resolving, JSON data responses, and presenter examples.  For complete applications with different structures, see [Demo applications](../start/demo-apps.md)."
